  "title": "Preschool Educator | Mother Tongue Language",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Plan, supervise and implement the programme for the class in accordance with Centre’s policies and framework.</li>\n  <li>Plan and prepare class projects, field trips and other experiential activities.</li>\n  <li>Develop and shape children’s character and moral values.</li>\n  <li>Ensure safety and hygiene of the children.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently as well as within a team.</li>\n  <li>Maintain good communication with the parents and Participate in parents’ discussion groups.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Possess <u><strong>ANY </strong></u>of the following ECDA certified Certificates</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Professional Diploma in Early Childhood Care and Education - Teaching (Chinese) (PDECCE-T/CL)</li>\n  <li>Diploma in Early Childhood Care and Education - Teaching (Chinese)(DECCE-T/CL)</li>\n  <li>Diploma (Conversion) in Early Childhood Care and Education - Teaching (Chinese)[(DECCE-T (Conversion) (CL)]</li>\n  <li>Certificate in Preschool Mother Tongue Language (Chinese)(CPMTL-C)</li>\n  <li>Certificate in Preschool Mother Tongue Language (Malay) (CPMTL-M)</li>\n  <li>Certificate in Preschool Mother Tongue Language (Tamil) (CPMTL-T)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Check out www.abercare.sg for more details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants may send in your resume to career@abercare.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
